{"tid":698663,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android P 新代號直接叫「Android 9」但不是9.0","createTime":"2018-06-12T01:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T15:30:50.000Z","uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff74b98402a1d74e2ce8863ea2e2cd45b8b7a4b","tid":698663,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，自 Android 系統誕生以來，Google 官方一直有將 Android 系統代號按照字母表的順序命名為一款甜品的習慣 ，上一代的 Android O 正是 Oreo，而最新的 Android P 也不例外，但是目前字母「P」具體代表的含義還不確定。在最新的 Android P 版本號中，Google 悄悄地想起修改為 Android 9。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/094220_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F094220_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8bea0ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令人不解的事，此次 Google 雖然將系統代號改為 Android 9 ，但卻不是傳統意義的「9.0」。另外，據稱在正式版來臨之前，Google 為用戶提供了一個彩蛋，也就是當用戶點擊版本號後會，就會出現一個 Android P 的彩蛋，聽起來好像很有趣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fnews%2F&d=%2F%2FKgto3ixgnKT515Xk6HvBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=05ecfe4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/news/</a>"},{"pid":"f1df1a7cf9d47a92dc568dfaa852503f1ae39757","tid":698663,"uid":182286,"like":11,"dislike":16,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f711514909b1d6f8b8face24cd0126359b1d38ab","tid":698663,"uid":2638,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:47:26.000Z","msg":"呢d 都當新聞😨<br />\n每日一個新聞都幾好搵"},{"pid":"30073ce836495e851209382da272a9d30e919945","tid":698663,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"Samsung Galaxy Note 9"},{"pid":"78673813255f3f7ee29305f794aa589dc29105ed","tid":698663,"uid":79355,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T07:39